  })), "\n\t", mdx("figcaption", {
    parentName: "figure"
  }, "Star Trail at 12,000 ft")), mdx("p", null, "Search on google for Startrail photography and you will find similar, amazing photos.\nAfter 11pm, it felt like someone drew over the sky and painted it pitch black, with a faint white layer of paint. Since it was full-moon time, stars disapear as the moon shines."), mdx("p", null, "We all left for Kasol the next day. Went to Manikaran Hot water bath. Thats for another post.\nWould encourage you to book the trek and go. Bookings start probably around September. But keep checking YHAIndia.org, these tickets get sold quickly.\nEnd of YHAI Sar Pass trekking diaries now!\nBye Bye!"));
